The Heist:
- Jam The Alarm
- Get Scissors
- Cut the wires to the Lazers
- Get Keycard/Code for Opening the Safe
- Open Safe
- Put money in bag more money less movement speed
- Get out with money



The Lab
- Start Dimension Machine (It blows the fuse all lights go out and doors close)
- hit the circuit breaker lights come on
- find the card/code to unlock all doors
- In one room there will be capacitors you need these to fix the machine however
  to get into that room you must switch off a broken generator that is electrocuting a puddle
- Next you must fuel the machine. There is a gantry arm holding plutonium navigate the arm to drop   the plutonium safely into the machine.
- Start the machine
- end game
